WEBVTT

00:02:26.146 --> 00:02:27.313
Happy birthday.

00:02:29.516 --> 00:02:30.851
You still don't eat this?

00:02:40.753 --> 00:02:42.464
Let's take a group picture.

00:02:45.631 --> 00:02:47.300
Even once-

00:02:50.047 --> 00:02:52.091
did you ever think of forgetting me?

00:02:52.138 --> 00:02:56.058
I never wished to forget you.

00:03:00.578 --> 00:03:01.660
I forgot to send this.

00:03:02.947 --> 00:03:04.741
Who's making you smile like that?

00:03:04.766 --> 00:03:06.768
You have a boyfriend now, don't you?

00:03:07.111 --> 00:03:08.074
Huh?

00:03:08.571 --> 00:03:09.989
A boyfriend?

00:03:09.989 --> 00:03:11.157
No, I don't have one.

00:03:13.034 --> 00:03:13.743
Kino-

00:03:13.743 --> 00:03:15.661
if you want,

00:03:16.179 --> 00:03:17.930
you can sleep here
next to me later.

00:03:17.955 --> 00:03:18.956
Don't worry about me.

00:04:36.387 --> 00:04:40.435
That love scene was so nuanced-
the passion, emotions, acting.

00:04:40.475 --> 00:04:42.477
I can’t be an actor.
I’d be asking what are we.

00:04:42.540 --> 00:04:44.709
Wow, Arclea. That was
intense but classy.

00:04:45.001 --> 00:04:47.107
That was worth the wait!

00:04:53.752 --> 00:04:55.770
Wow, you can
really feel that Arkin's

00:04:55.794 --> 00:04:58.318
feelings for Clea are
genuine in that scene!

00:04:59.974 --> 00:05:04.645
I swear, they're still a thing!
Once it's confirmed, I'll totally faint.

00:05:11.360 --> 00:05:12.653
How's the movie?

00:05:15.072 --> 00:05:16.071
Huh?

00:05:16.908 --> 00:05:17.909
It's good.

00:05:19.952 --> 00:05:20.745
The movie was so good.

00:05:20.745 --> 00:05:22.788
You and Clea were so cute together.

00:05:25.294 --> 00:05:27.796
You really like her, huh?

00:05:30.796 --> 00:05:32.006
I saw your eyes.

00:05:33.883 --> 00:05:36.594
And it's impossible not to like her.

00:05:36.594 --> 00:05:39.430
Everyone sees her as perfect, and-

00:05:39.972 --> 00:05:42.475
you always do scenes like that.

00:05:43.142 --> 00:05:45.728
Any man would fall
for a girl like her,

00:05:46.354 --> 00:05:47.605
actor or not.

00:05:53.778 --> 00:05:55.655
Where is that coming from?

00:05:58.658 --> 00:06:01.827
You looked at her the way
you used to look at me.

00:06:07.882 --> 00:06:11.136
I think you didn't
watch the movie carefully then.

00:06:16.092 --> 00:06:17.885
Do you really not like her?

00:06:18.469 --> 00:06:22.139
I mean, you've spent
so much time together.

00:06:22.765 --> 00:06:24.642
You really haven't fallen for her?

00:06:27.979 --> 00:06:30.481
If time could measure
my love for someone,

00:06:31.399 --> 00:06:34.151
think about who I've been
with for more than 20 years.

00:06:38.489 --> 00:06:40.408
Then you have your answer.

00:06:51.377 --> 00:06:52.294
I was-

00:06:52.753 --> 00:06:54.255
I was just asking.

00:07:04.849 --> 00:07:06.851
The movie was really good.

00:07:06.851 --> 00:07:07.893
- Yeah!
- Yes!

00:07:07.893 --> 00:07:08.853
- Wow.
- Amazing.

00:07:08.853 --> 00:07:10.104
- Just wow.
- Really great.

00:07:10.104 --> 00:07:12.064
- I really felt it.
- It was great.

00:07:12.064 --> 00:07:13.482
- Best actor award.
- I approve.

00:07:13.482 --> 00:07:15.151
- No, and also the best-
- Yeah. That's it.

00:07:15.151 --> 00:07:17.653
- I was tearing up during the crying scene.
- You're right.

00:07:17.653 --> 00:07:21.198
- Most of your fans talk so fancy, too.
- Let's eat now. The food's getting cold.

00:07:21.198 --> 00:07:23.159
- Okay.
- It's already cold.

00:07:23.159 --> 00:07:23.993
Give me some.

00:07:23.993 --> 00:07:25.261
You don't have your drink yet.

00:07:25.286 --> 00:07:26.829
Yanna, can I have some of that?

00:07:43.163 --> 00:07:44.179
There.

00:07:45.639 --> 00:07:47.183
The string's been replaced.

00:07:48.100 --> 00:07:49.393
Thanks.

00:07:49.518 --> 00:07:51.937
I bought these strings
a long time ago.

00:07:51.937 --> 00:07:54.315
I just never got
around to changing them.

00:07:55.475 --> 00:08:01.898
Maybe your guitar was just waiting
for the right time for you to use it again.

00:08:03.115 --> 00:08:04.200
You think so?

00:08:04.658 --> 00:08:05.993
Just my theory.

00:08:10.105 --> 00:08:11.940
By the way, Via-

00:08:12.541 --> 00:08:16.337
The release party for my
new single is pushing through.

00:08:16.754 --> 00:08:18.297
Can you come?

00:08:20.341 --> 00:08:23.928
I don't think I'm ready to go
somewhere with a lot of people yet.

00:08:25.221 --> 00:08:26.597
It's just a small gig.

00:08:26.597 --> 00:08:28.641
Only close friends.
There won't be many people.

00:08:31.977 --> 00:08:34.313
I mean, really just
close friends, I promise.

00:08:35.272 --> 00:08:36.190
All right, how about this?

00:08:36.190 --> 00:08:37.870
If what I'm saying isn't true,

00:08:37.894 --> 00:08:39.985
you can ignore me forever and
never talk to me again.

00:08:41.537 --> 00:08:45.234
I just want the people
I love to be there

00:08:45.906 --> 00:08:48.244
when I celebrate the
release of my new song.

00:08:52.219 --> 00:08:53.332
I'll see.

00:08:57.075 --> 00:08:59.414
Can you squeeze me into your schedule,

00:09:00.047 --> 00:09:01.799
Architect Diaz?

00:09:01.799 --> 00:09:02.967
Maybe you can do something about it?

00:09:03.759 --> 00:09:05.553
Talk to my manager.

00:09:12.101 --> 00:09:13.144
Hold on.

00:09:14.886 --> 00:09:15.781
Oh.

00:09:16.689 --> 00:09:17.815
The live stream...

00:09:20.192 --> 00:09:21.152
Hi guys!

00:09:21.152 --> 00:09:22.945
Long time no live.

00:09:22.945 --> 00:09:24.488
Wow, it's been so long
since the last one, right?

00:09:24.488 --> 00:09:25.570
But this will be quick.

00:09:28.742 --> 00:09:29.869
Question.

00:09:30.619 --> 00:09:31.620
Where are you right now?

00:09:31.620 --> 00:09:33.080
I'm in my room.

00:09:33.789 --> 00:09:36.542
I'm in the room...

00:09:37.006 --> 00:09:39.467
on set where we're shooting.

00:09:40.921 --> 00:09:41.797
Look at this.

00:09:41.797 --> 00:09:42.631
See?

00:09:44.816 --> 00:09:46.401
Here's another question.

00:09:46.986 --> 00:09:49.572
Is Clea your girlfriend?

00:09:49.597 --> 00:09:51.724
Is Clea my girlfriend?

00:09:54.518 --> 00:09:55.508
No.

00:09:55.853 --> 00:09:57.438
I don't have a girlfriend yet.

00:10:00.566 --> 00:10:03.027
Well, if some of you want to apply,

00:10:03.027 --> 00:10:04.737
I'd be willing to entertain.

00:10:05.237 --> 00:10:06.530
Just let me know.

00:10:07.865 --> 00:10:10.367
Since when did he
learn to flirt with his fans?

00:10:10.367 --> 00:10:11.493
Here's another.

00:10:12.494 --> 00:10:14.872
Do you like someone right now?

00:10:16.297 --> 00:10:19.008
Do I like someone right now?

00:10:21.788 --> 00:10:24.290
Do I like someone right now?

00:10:25.218 --> 00:10:26.266
Of course.

00:10:28.761 --> 00:10:30.179
I like you guys.

00:10:31.055 --> 00:10:32.640
My Rhythmics.

00:10:35.893 --> 00:10:36.922
By the way-

00:10:37.303 --> 00:10:39.806
I hope you guys
will like my new song.

00:10:40.731 --> 00:10:44.151
It's about reminiscing
memories with someone special

00:10:44.526 --> 00:10:45.653
who eventually left.

00:10:50.225 --> 00:10:53.520
The song expresses how painful it was.

00:10:58.506 --> 00:10:59.590
No.

00:11:00.120 --> 00:11:01.830
No, it's not my experience.

00:11:02.753 --> 00:11:05.130
It's the experience of a friend of mine.

00:11:05.130 --> 00:11:06.674
If you guys only knew...

00:11:07.700 --> 00:11:10.203
All of my friends are heartbroken.

00:11:10.511 --> 00:11:11.428
So, that's it.

00:11:11.428 --> 00:11:13.222
Shoutout to you, Sebastian!

00:11:13.912 --> 00:11:15.831
If you're listening right now,

00:11:16.517 --> 00:11:17.518
poor you.

00:11:17.643 --> 00:11:19.311
This song is for you.

00:11:21.104 --> 00:11:23.022
Is it really for someone else?

00:11:23.743 --> 00:11:25.662
Or is it actually for me?

00:11:32.908 --> 00:11:37.204
Kino, there's somewhere I want
to go tomorrow. Are you free?

00:11:37.204 --> 00:11:39.623
Are you asking
me out on a date?

00:11:39.623 --> 00:11:41.583
Just answer me.

00:11:42.454 --> 00:11:45.207
For you, Via, I'm available.

00:11:59.322 --> 00:12:00.323
Hello?

00:12:00.811 --> 00:12:03.314
Via, are you asleep?

00:12:04.565 --> 00:12:05.899
Not yet. Why?

00:12:07.307 --> 00:12:10.435
I just wanted to ask what time
I should go to your place tomorrow.

00:12:10.779 --> 00:12:12.214
5:00 AM?

00:12:12.239 --> 00:12:13.416
That's too early.

00:12:13.441 --> 00:12:17.362
Maybe around 3:00 PM?

00:12:20.581 --> 00:12:22.541
All right, 10:00 AM then,
so I won't be late.

00:12:22.541 --> 00:12:23.542
10:00 AM?

00:12:24.076 --> 00:12:25.202
That's still too early.

00:12:25.669 --> 00:12:27.838
Well, I'm planning to
have lunch at your place.

00:12:27.838 --> 00:12:30.132
I told you it's too early.

00:12:30.132 --> 00:12:32.634
Just come by 3:00 PM.
I still have errands in the morning.

00:12:33.267 --> 00:12:35.770
Okay, fine. 3:00 PM.

00:12:36.753 --> 00:12:37.799
Is that all?

00:12:39.099 --> 00:12:40.684
I have one more question for you.

00:12:41.185 --> 00:12:42.135
What is it?

00:12:43.937 --> 00:12:45.072
Have you eaten?

00:12:48.609 --> 00:12:49.902
Yes. Why?

00:12:51.070 --> 00:12:53.572
Nothing. Just asking.

00:12:55.199 --> 00:12:58.243
Arkin, it's almost midnight.

00:12:58.243 --> 00:12:59.328
Go to sleep.

00:12:59.328 --> 00:13:01.205
Last one. Just one last thing.

00:13:01.205 --> 00:13:02.915
What now?

00:13:02.915 --> 00:13:04.917
I'll be there at 2:30 PM tomorrow, okay?

00:13:04.917 --> 00:13:06.919
Is that all right?
That's my final bargain.

00:13:07.211 --> 00:13:08.212
Arkin.

00:13:08.212 --> 00:13:10.923
Okay, okay. Go rest now.

00:13:10.948 --> 00:13:12.027
Good night.

00:13:12.883 --> 00:13:14.259
Good night, Avianna.

00:13:16.970 --> 00:13:18.430
Good night, Larkin.

00:13:22.684 --> 00:13:24.645
All right, go to sleep. Bye now.

00:13:25.187 --> 00:13:26.188
Okay, okay.

00:13:26.397 --> 00:13:27.773
You want me to
hang up the call?

00:13:27.773 --> 00:13:29.274
Fine, I'll hang up now.

00:13:29.441 --> 00:13:30.943
I'm hanging up. Go to sleep.

00:13:31.125 --> 00:13:32.751
Okay. Bye.

00:13:32.986 --> 00:13:34.613
Good night!

00:13:47.334 --> 00:13:48.787
Such a kid.

00:13:50.087 --> 00:13:51.755
So clingy.

00:13:53.715 --> 00:13:55.092
Just like before.

00:13:55.259 --> 00:13:56.885
Good night, Via.

00:13:58.804 --> 00:14:00.472
Good night, Via.

00:14:13.430 --> 00:14:15.474
So this is where you
decided to take me on a date?

00:14:15.863 --> 00:14:16.947
At my school?

00:14:17.828 --> 00:14:19.324
I was just here earlier.

00:14:20.698 --> 00:14:22.033
Then let's just go home. Come on.

00:14:22.058 --> 00:14:23.643
I'm kidding. Relax.

00:14:25.122 --> 00:14:27.063
It just reminded me of our college days.

00:14:27.624 --> 00:14:29.877
Well, technically I'm still in college.

00:14:30.776 --> 00:14:33.028
Why were you at
school today anyway?

00:14:33.213 --> 00:14:34.882
It's the weekend. Do you have class?

00:14:35.399 --> 00:14:39.720
We shot a school-related project earlier.

00:14:40.262 --> 00:14:42.473
And I was the director.

00:14:43.974 --> 00:14:46.477
Oh, wow. Look at you.

00:14:47.728 --> 00:14:49.813
What do you enjoy more?

00:14:50.147 --> 00:14:52.274
Being off-cam or on-cam?

00:14:55.068 --> 00:14:56.236
Off-cam.

00:14:58.113 --> 00:15:00.782
It's really more fun
working behind the camera.

00:15:01.825 --> 00:15:04.411
That was your original dream, right?

00:15:04.995 --> 00:15:06.497
To become a director.

00:15:08.248 --> 00:15:09.791
But what about your music?

00:15:11.736 --> 00:15:13.571
I still love music.

00:15:14.908 --> 00:15:17.244
I don't need to act
when it comes to music.

00:15:17.817 --> 00:15:20.028
I can be who I want to be.

00:15:20.636 --> 00:15:22.054
I can be myself,

00:15:22.930 --> 00:15:24.223
and that's what matters.

00:15:25.974 --> 00:15:28.477
I'm tired of acting
in front of the camera, Via.

00:15:29.603 --> 00:15:32.314
I want to be genuine through my music.

00:15:36.360 --> 00:15:40.614
I'm glad it's clear to him now
which direction he wants to take.

00:15:40.976 --> 00:15:42.644
What about me?

00:16:17.150 --> 00:16:18.318
Go on.

00:16:21.488 --> 00:16:22.573
Fine, I'll start.

00:16:25.075 --> 00:16:26.326
Sing with me, okay?

00:16:31.540 --> 00:16:32.624
Like old times.

00:16:46.305 --> 00:16:51.310
♪ Left thinking in the
midst of the chaos, ♪

00:16:52.102 --> 00:16:57.733
♪ utterly bewildered by these feelings. ♪

00:16:58.191 --> 00:17:02.112
♪ I can't tell if this is a dream, ♪

00:17:03.053 --> 00:17:09.553
♪ as if my heart was
playing in the heavens. ♪

00:17:09.578 --> 00:17:15.709
♪ - In the daylight you are there, ♪
♪ - In the daylight you are there, ♪

00:17:15.709 --> 00:17:20.922
♪ - beside me, and I gaze at you. ♪
♪ - beside me, and I gaze at you. ♪

00:17:21.857 --> 00:17:27.029
♪ - I don't know anymore, I get confused ♪
♪ - I don't know anymore, I get confused ♪

00:17:27.054 --> 00:17:32.100
♪ - whenever I'm with you in... ♪
♪ - whenever I'm with you in... ♪

00:17:32.893 --> 00:17:40.067
♪ - A golden scenery beneath the sky, ♪
♪ - A golden scenery beneath the sky, ♪

00:17:40.275 --> 00:17:44.279
♪ - having you with me. ♪
♪ - having you with me. ♪

00:17:44.755 --> 00:17:48.634
♪ - As the wind blows, ♪
♪ - As the wind blows, ♪

00:17:48.659 --> 00:17:51.963
♪ along with the song, ♪

00:17:51.994 --> 00:17:55.298
♪ I feel your hand. ♪

00:17:55.582 --> 00:18:02.547
♪ - May my prayer be heard, ♪
♪ - May my prayer be heard, ♪

00:18:02.756 --> 00:18:06.760
♪ - that you love me in return. ♪
♪ - that you love me in return. ♪

00:18:06.843 --> 00:18:10.889
♪ - An orange sky, ♪
♪ - An orange sky, ♪

00:18:10.889 --> 00:18:18.438
♪ - painting the beauty of your eyes. ♪
♪ - painting the beauty of your eyes. ♪

00:18:36.164 --> 00:18:37.290
Via.

00:18:43.046 --> 00:18:44.464
Kino.

00:18:47.134 --> 00:18:48.927
You're still the same, Via.

00:19:49.039 --> 00:19:50.226
Say it, Rye.

00:19:52.908 --> 00:19:56.119
I wanna write music, Kino.

00:20:13.408 --> 00:20:16.453
So, Via, what's your initial idea
for the song you want to write?

00:20:16.570 --> 00:20:19.114
Do you already have
a beat or melody in mind?

00:20:19.184 --> 00:20:21.603
There are drums here if you
want something with a bit of a beat-

00:20:21.628 --> 00:20:22.437
Do you want it upbeat?

00:20:22.437 --> 00:20:24.851
Or there's a guitar if you prefer
an acoustic or electric sound.

00:20:24.876 --> 00:20:25.877
What do you need?

00:20:26.525 --> 00:20:27.734
Let's start.

00:20:30.320 --> 00:20:34.616
I usually have ideas
that come to mind.

00:20:35.992 --> 00:20:37.661
But right now, I don't
know. It feels like...

00:20:37.911 --> 00:20:40.080
It feels like my mind is blank.

00:20:41.122 --> 00:20:44.501
I really can't think of anything.
I think I'm still scared.

00:20:46.586 --> 00:20:47.671
Scared of what?

00:20:48.839 --> 00:20:52.175
That if I start writing a song,

00:20:53.301 --> 00:20:54.886
I might realize...

00:20:55.262 --> 00:20:56.863
it's not meant for me after all.

00:20:57.389 --> 00:21:00.141
When I start writing a song,

00:21:00.738 --> 00:21:04.555
I might realize that
I'm not good at it either.

00:21:12.020 --> 00:21:13.605
Do you think...

00:21:14.090 --> 00:21:16.300
I liked the first song I ever wrote?

00:21:17.963 --> 00:21:20.466
Honestly, I'm already so
sick of that song.

00:21:21.739 --> 00:21:23.240
Well, before,

00:21:23.373 --> 00:21:24.165
I thought it was amazing.

00:21:24.165 --> 00:21:25.917
That's why I used
to brag about it to you.

00:21:27.252 --> 00:21:29.963
But I knew that wasn't
all I was capable of.

00:21:31.172 --> 00:21:33.216
Everyone starts with something.

00:21:33.550 --> 00:21:36.261
Just because you don't like
what you're starting with,

00:21:36.803 --> 00:21:39.014
doesn't mean you won't
like what comes next.

00:21:43.268 --> 00:21:45.020
Do you think...

00:21:46.146 --> 00:21:48.064
you're good at music now?

00:21:49.656 --> 00:21:51.617
Good at music?

00:21:51.645 --> 00:21:52.688
Yeah.

00:21:54.070 --> 00:21:55.800
Because I believe in myself.

00:21:56.742 --> 00:21:58.952
But I also know I'm not the best.

00:22:00.076 --> 00:22:01.661
And I know I can still be better.

00:22:02.454 --> 00:22:04.956
A person's growth never really ends.

00:22:06.330 --> 00:22:11.043
I know there's still so
much I can do and achieve.

00:22:11.588 --> 00:22:12.756
As long as

00:22:13.423 --> 00:22:16.843
I don't limit myself to my comfort zone.

00:22:17.344 --> 00:22:18.595
And don't worry.

00:22:18.620 --> 00:22:20.956
That's why I'm here. To guide you.

00:22:21.702 --> 00:22:23.495
Just like how you
guided me before.

00:22:25.185 --> 00:22:27.020
I told you,

00:22:27.896 --> 00:22:31.107
you made me want to
learn music and embrace it.

00:22:31.942 --> 00:22:32.609
Okay?

00:22:37.572 --> 00:22:39.574
Haven't I told you this before?

00:22:42.452 --> 00:22:43.495
Thank you.

00:22:52.921 --> 00:22:55.256
I won't kiss you but-

00:22:57.634 --> 00:22:59.719
I'll save it for a better time.

00:23:07.143 --> 00:23:08.144
I have an idea.

00:23:08.812 --> 00:23:09.396
What?

00:23:09.604 --> 00:23:10.730
I'll just organize it.

00:23:11.147 --> 00:23:13.233
All right. That's a good start.

00:23:13.650 --> 00:23:14.901
I'll leave you here for now.

00:23:15.360 --> 00:23:16.695
Just let me know
when you need me, okay?

00:23:16.695 --> 00:23:18.321
When you need a fresh idea or...

00:23:18.405 --> 00:23:19.531
- Just tell me, okay?
- Yeah.

00:23:19.531 --> 00:23:20.865
- I'll be right here, okay?
- Yeah.

00:23:20.865 --> 00:23:21.700
Just call me.

00:23:21.700 --> 00:23:22.659
Yeah, okay.

00:23:30.333 --> 00:23:31.876
All done? What have you come up with?

00:23:32.210 --> 00:23:33.503
I haven't called you yet.

00:23:33.670 --> 00:23:34.421
Oh, okay.

00:23:37.799 --> 00:23:39.050
It's beautiful. Really beautiful.

00:23:39.050 --> 00:23:39.968
Let's start?

00:23:40.218 --> 00:23:41.386
What's the first lyric?

00:23:41.386 --> 00:23:42.095
I said I'd call you...

00:23:42.095 --> 00:23:43.513
- I'll call you.
- Oh, okay.

00:23:47.892 --> 00:23:49.811
Not yet, Kino.

00:24:09.247 --> 00:24:10.242
Yeah.

00:24:10.582 --> 00:24:11.249
This is it.

00:24:11.249 --> 00:24:12.208
There.

00:24:12.208 --> 00:24:13.242
Right?

00:24:13.626 --> 00:24:14.727
Yeah.

00:25:41.154 --> 00:25:42.030
There you go.

00:25:42.055 --> 00:25:43.681
Oh, that's amazing.

00:25:45.802 --> 00:25:47.470
Then you can put-

00:25:47.470 --> 00:25:49.931
This here, to bring it all back. There.

00:25:53.993 --> 00:25:56.746
Via, thank you so much!

00:25:56.771 --> 00:26:00.358
My flight got moved suddenly.
I'll get you a souvenir.

00:26:03.525 --> 00:26:07.279
It's okay. I'm not too busy anyway.

00:26:09.617 --> 00:26:10.660
Can I see it?

00:26:14.747 --> 00:26:19.335
Oh, right. I haven't told Kino yet
that I won't be able to go see him.

00:26:20.125 --> 00:26:22.294
Via, let's have lunch
before we leave.

00:26:22.380 --> 00:26:24.465
- Hey, Avi!
- Uncle Arkin!

00:26:24.465 --> 00:26:25.800
You're here!

00:26:25.800 --> 00:26:27.677
Give me a hug. Here.

00:26:30.096 --> 00:26:32.223
I should have told you earlier.

00:26:32.223 --> 00:26:36.186
We might need to reschedule
today's music session.

00:26:36.975 --> 00:26:38.346
All right. Okay, sure.

00:26:39.981 --> 00:26:44.110
Aunt Via, mommy told me
you were going out for lunch.

00:26:46.321 --> 00:26:49.365
Yanna really says all sorts
of things to the kid, huh.

00:26:49.949 --> 00:26:51.117
Please?

00:26:51.117 --> 00:26:53.203
Of course, we'll eat out. My treat.

00:26:53.369 --> 00:26:55.538
For my favorite niece.

00:26:55.538 --> 00:26:56.372
What do you want to eat?

00:26:56.789 --> 00:26:57.498
Noodles.

00:26:57.498 --> 00:26:59.167
Oh, let's eat noodles then. Come on.

00:26:59.167 --> 00:27:00.210
I'm hungry.

00:27:00.460 --> 00:27:01.628
- Let's go.
- Yeah, come on.

00:27:01.628 --> 00:27:03.129
Bring your tablet, okay?

00:27:03.129 --> 00:27:04.172
- Here. Is this Avi's?
- Yes.

00:27:04.172 --> 00:27:04.814
All right, let's go.

00:27:04.839 --> 00:27:06.132
- Come on, Avi.
- I got it.

00:27:06.583 --> 00:27:07.480
Uncle's got it.

00:27:08.140 --> 00:27:09.238
Let's go.

00:27:16.948 --> 00:27:18.408
Do you want anything else?

00:27:23.548 --> 00:27:25.007
- Aunt Via...
- Yeah?

00:27:25.032 --> 00:27:27.118
Why isn't Uncle Arkin
sitting with us?

00:27:27.143 --> 00:27:28.603
Did you two fight?

00:27:28.863 --> 00:27:31.366
Please don't fight. Fighting is bad.

00:27:33.167 --> 00:27:35.670
This is how Mom and Dad fight, too.

00:27:38.623 --> 00:27:41.626
Avi, no. We did not fight.

00:27:42.460 --> 00:27:44.963
Uncle Arkin is just
hiding from people.

00:27:45.463 --> 00:27:46.756
But why?

00:27:47.590 --> 00:27:49.259
He is seen everywhere.

00:27:50.885 --> 00:27:52.470
I know.

00:27:52.470 --> 00:27:56.387
But he can't be seen sitting with us.

00:27:56.574 --> 00:27:59.410
Because his fans might
get the wrong idea.

00:27:59.435 --> 00:28:01.354
You know what I mean, right?

00:28:01.354 --> 00:28:03.356
Just like with your Auntie.

00:28:05.175 --> 00:28:06.844
I see.

00:28:07.086 --> 00:28:09.588
But he looks so lonely.

00:28:12.913 --> 00:28:17.293
Uncle Arkin, when you're famous,
can't you join your loved ones to eat?

00:28:17.318 --> 00:28:19.070
Is it really a bad thing?

00:28:19.095 --> 00:28:21.263
Why would your fans get mad?

00:28:26.838 --> 00:28:29.340
Those are such deep questions.

00:28:29.480 --> 00:28:32.828
Kind of a mix of Yanna and Sam.

00:28:33.511 --> 00:28:34.679
How should I answer that...

00:28:35.505 --> 00:28:37.090
Sit with us please.

00:28:37.115 --> 00:28:38.950
I rarely see you.

00:28:38.975 --> 00:28:41.478
I just want to eat lunch with you.

00:28:45.315 --> 00:28:46.371
It's okay.

00:28:46.908 --> 00:28:48.334
There aren't many people anyway.

00:28:48.359 --> 00:28:50.194
And you're an endorser here, right?

00:28:51.543 --> 00:28:52.637
All right, come on.

00:28:52.811 --> 00:28:53.785
I'll move over there.

00:28:55.116 --> 00:28:56.019
Let's go.

00:29:00.621 --> 00:29:03.124
That looks delicious.

00:29:05.376 --> 00:29:06.502
Is that for me?

00:29:08.880 --> 00:29:10.381
Oh, me too?

00:29:11.549 --> 00:29:12.467
Thank you.

00:29:12.467 --> 00:29:13.676
Of course, for Avi, too.

00:29:13.676 --> 00:29:14.594
Here you go.

00:29:21.722 --> 00:29:22.557
Yum. You like it?

00:29:22.582 --> 00:29:23.416
Eat more.

00:29:24.328 --> 00:29:28.791
Mommy said food tastes yummier
if I share it with my family.

00:29:37.200 --> 00:29:38.326
What else do you want?

00:29:38.493 --> 00:29:41.204
Ask Uncle Arkin if he
wants some sushi rolls.

00:29:43.081 --> 00:29:43.915
Do you want some?

00:29:43.915 --> 00:29:45.208
Yeah, sure. Okay.

00:29:50.129 --> 00:29:51.255
All right, then.

00:29:59.222 --> 00:30:00.264
Here. go ahead.

00:30:00.264 --> 00:30:01.516
One, two, three, go.

00:30:03.059 --> 00:30:04.143
There.

00:30:04.852 --> 00:30:06.896
One, two, three, go.

00:30:10.655 --> 00:30:12.282
Uncle Arkin,

00:30:13.277 --> 00:30:15.321
do you like Aunt Via?

00:30:18.783 --> 00:30:20.618
I love your Aunt, of course.

00:30:20.952 --> 00:30:23.329
But she doesn't know
if she loves me or not.

00:30:25.915 --> 00:30:27.166
Of course, she does.

00:30:27.500 --> 00:30:31.629
She looks at you the way
Mommy looks at Daddy.

00:30:39.387 --> 00:30:42.056
Aunt Via, can I get cookies?

00:30:42.181 --> 00:30:43.391
Of course.

00:30:43.391 --> 00:30:44.600
Just get them from the pantry.

00:30:44.600 --> 00:30:46.269
You know where they are, right?

00:30:48.938 --> 00:30:50.189
Thank you.

00:30:53.109 --> 00:30:55.278
Kids these days, huh?

00:30:56.946 --> 00:30:58.614
- Via.
- Yeah?

00:31:00.119 --> 00:31:01.996
I don't think I've asked you yet,

00:31:03.334 --> 00:31:05.086
do you plan on having kids?

00:31:05.580 --> 00:31:06.956
Just curious.

00:31:10.084 --> 00:31:11.172
No.

00:31:13.045 --> 00:31:14.250
Okay.

00:31:17.398 --> 00:31:19.442
Aren't you going to ask why?

00:31:21.095 --> 00:31:22.638
That's your choice, Via.

00:31:23.178 --> 00:31:28.475
I shouldn't question your decision
about your body or yourself.

00:31:34.650 --> 00:31:36.319
I'm scared.

00:31:37.298 --> 00:31:39.217
I feel like...

00:31:40.510 --> 00:31:42.804
I won't be a good mother.

00:31:44.013 --> 00:31:46.933
I'm afraid I might
turn out like my mom.

00:31:47.934 --> 00:31:51.896
Especially now that
I want to enter her world.

00:31:57.026 --> 00:32:00.363
Via, do you remember
the promise you made before?

00:32:01.197 --> 00:32:03.866
That you wouldn't live
in the past anymore.

00:32:04.909 --> 00:32:07.286
Live in the present
and stop limiting yourself

00:32:07.286 --> 00:32:09.747
with the future you're
imagining in your head.

00:32:10.498 --> 00:32:13.543
Make decisions for yourself,
not out of fear,

00:32:13.709 --> 00:32:15.711
but because you
truly want them.

00:32:16.254 --> 00:32:19.549
It doesn't matter to me what you
choose because I understand.

00:32:20.591 --> 00:32:22.093
I'll be with you

00:32:22.552 --> 00:32:25.138
until you face all the
things you're afraid of.

00:32:25.596 --> 00:32:28.099
We agreed to work
on it together, right?

00:32:35.231 --> 00:32:36.232
Kino.

00:32:38.443 --> 00:32:40.611
You've really grown so much.

00:32:41.195 --> 00:32:42.822
I'm proud of you.

00:33:04.927 --> 00:33:05.553
Hi!

00:33:05.553 --> 00:33:06.554
- Hi!
- Oh.

00:33:06.554 --> 00:33:09.515
- Hello. Thank you.
- Glad your flight wasn't delayed.

00:33:09.765 --> 00:33:10.808
- No.
- Come on in.

00:33:10.808 --> 00:33:12.768
So far, everything's okay.

00:33:15.354 --> 00:33:18.316
Hey, thank you for
taking care of my kid.

00:33:18.858 --> 00:33:20.735
I'll promote your movie. I promise.

00:33:21.444 --> 00:33:23.196
That's right. I like that.

00:33:24.530 --> 00:33:25.606
Where's Avi?

00:33:25.948 --> 00:33:28.951
Upstairs, brushing her teeth.
She ate a lot of sweets.

00:33:29.452 --> 00:33:31.537
Speaking of the movie...

00:33:33.039 --> 00:33:34.332
Is it true about that-

00:33:34.999 --> 00:33:36.751
the bed scene with Clea?

00:33:38.628 --> 00:33:40.004
What? Of course not.

00:33:40.463 --> 00:33:42.173
Besides, nothing was seen anyway.

00:33:42.632 --> 00:33:44.592
I'll go pick up Avi upstairs.

00:33:48.686 --> 00:33:51.105
In fairness, they were great there.

00:33:51.265 --> 00:33:52.892
Hey, Via. Don't hold back, okay?

00:33:52.892 --> 00:33:54.060
Do your best!

00:33:54.385 --> 00:33:55.845
Enough with the cute act.

00:33:56.312 --> 00:33:58.105
Come on, Yanna, not again.

00:33:58.231 --> 00:33:59.482
But weren't you...

00:33:59.482 --> 00:34:01.859
Aren't you annoyed
seeing that bed scene?

00:34:09.283 --> 00:34:11.702
Wait, I have something for you.

00:34:18.501 --> 00:34:20.836
Yanna!

00:34:20.920 --> 00:34:21.921
Not again.

00:34:22.171 --> 00:34:23.214
Here's more.

00:34:23.974 --> 00:34:24.975
And more.

00:34:26.008 --> 00:34:28.386
Take more so it's extra safe.

00:34:28.636 --> 00:34:29.929
Double protection.

00:34:29.929 --> 00:34:31.055
Here, there are some dotted-

00:34:31.055 --> 00:34:32.682
Mommy!

00:34:33.224 --> 00:34:35.810
Hi, baby! Let's go home, okay?

00:34:37.019 --> 00:34:38.779
- Daddy cooked dinner.
- Yanna.

00:34:38.852 --> 00:34:39.747
Your bag.

00:34:39.772 --> 00:34:40.982
Thank you.

00:34:42.441 --> 00:34:44.277
All right, we'll go ahead.

00:34:44.527 --> 00:34:45.695
Thanks again.

00:34:45.695 --> 00:34:46.529
- Bye.
- Bye.

00:34:46.529 --> 00:34:47.905
- Take care!
- Did you have fun?

00:34:47.989 --> 00:34:48.990
Thank you.

00:34:48.990 --> 00:34:50.157
Thanks a lot.

00:34:50.157 --> 00:34:51.534
- Did you enjoy, Avi?
- Let me carry it, baby.

00:34:51.534 --> 00:34:53.160
Ah, the ukulele.

00:34:53.744 --> 00:34:54.808
Get it, baby.

00:34:55.121 --> 00:34:56.414
- Say, thank you.
- Thank you.

00:34:56.581 --> 00:34:57.540
Thank you.

00:34:57.540 --> 00:34:58.457
- Let's go.
- Come on.

00:34:58.457 --> 00:35:00.293
- Thank you.
- Bye.

00:35:00.293 --> 00:35:01.460
- Bye, Avi.

00:35:01.460 --> 00:35:02.837
Come back, okay?

00:35:03.087 --> 00:35:05.172
Did you learn something
from Uncle Arkin?

00:35:05.172 --> 00:35:05.965
Yes.

00:35:05.965 --> 00:35:07.508
Play for me, okay? Thanks, guys!

00:35:07.592 --> 00:35:09.093
- Bye.
- Take care.

00:35:09.427 --> 00:35:10.720
- Bye!
- Bye.

00:35:10.720 --> 00:35:11.304
Take care.

00:35:11.304 --> 00:35:12.263
Bye, Avi!

00:35:12.263 --> 00:35:13.431
Bye!

00:35:25.401 --> 00:35:26.485
Via, are you okay?

00:35:26.485 --> 00:35:27.236
Huh?

00:35:28.613 --> 00:35:29.697
Of course.

00:35:31.616 --> 00:35:32.550
Okay.

00:35:33.242 --> 00:35:34.327
By the way, tomorrow

00:35:34.327 --> 00:35:36.954
I have a commercial shoot
in the morning with Director Victor.

00:35:36.954 --> 00:35:38.456
Do you know him?
The famous director?

00:35:38.456 --> 00:35:39.248
Yes.

00:35:39.248 --> 00:35:41.083
Maybe you'd like to do a set visit.

00:35:41.375 --> 00:35:44.128
It's just for a short while,
only one scene, then it's done.

00:35:45.755 --> 00:35:46.691
All right.

00:35:47.423 --> 00:35:49.133
Okay, I'll pick you up.

00:35:49.967 --> 00:35:50.995
Sure.

00:36:12.990 --> 00:36:15.785
- Let's eat first.
- Thank you.

00:36:15.785 --> 00:36:16.911
How's everything going there?

00:36:16.911 --> 00:36:18.454
- All good?
- Yeah.

00:36:18.454 --> 00:36:21.374
Just make sure all the
materials are complete, okay?

00:36:23.668 --> 00:36:24.335
Oh.

00:36:24.335 --> 00:36:25.353
Hi.

00:36:25.378 --> 00:36:26.921
- You're here.
- Following up from the head office.

00:36:26.921 --> 00:36:27.380
Okay.

00:36:27.380 --> 00:36:28.714
- Hi!
- We need to confirm this.

00:36:28.714 --> 00:36:29.965
- How are you?
- I'm good.

00:36:29.965 --> 00:36:31.133
Glad you dropped by.

00:36:31.133 --> 00:36:32.510
- I have a shoot nearby.
- What's up?

00:36:32.510 --> 00:36:35.971
Architect Diaz and Architect Dan are here.

00:36:37.348 --> 00:36:39.325
You should've brought some food.

00:36:39.350 --> 00:36:41.560
That's why I'm here, to eat.

00:36:42.520 --> 00:36:43.667
Hi, Via.

00:36:44.480 --> 00:36:45.511
Hello.

00:36:46.273 --> 00:36:47.152
Hello...

00:36:48.025 --> 00:36:49.193
Are you okay?

00:36:49.819 --> 00:36:51.529
Did you two fight again?

00:36:52.446 --> 00:36:53.155
No, we're fine.

00:36:53.155 --> 00:36:54.448
What's for lunch here?

00:36:54.824 --> 00:36:57.743
The length of this is okay, right?

00:36:58.035 --> 00:36:59.245
There's food on set, though.

00:37:00.705 --> 00:37:03.082
- I want the food here, maybe it's good.
- Seems fine already, right?

00:37:03.624 --> 00:37:06.544
By the way, how was
your shoot yesterday?

00:37:06.544 --> 00:37:07.545
And...

00:37:08.671 --> 00:37:09.839
Speaking of...

00:37:10.423 --> 00:37:11.257
Looks okay-

00:37:11.282 --> 00:37:12.408
It was good.

00:37:12.870 --> 00:37:15.164
The dressing room was so nice.

00:37:17.430 --> 00:37:18.305
I'm sorry.

00:37:18.305 --> 00:37:19.473
- Are you okay?
- You okay?

00:37:19.473 --> 00:37:21.892
- Yes, I'm okay.
- Are you really okay? You look flushed.

00:37:22.268 --> 00:37:23.034
No.

00:37:23.059 --> 00:37:24.186
- I'm okay.
- As I was saying,

00:37:24.186 --> 00:37:26.689
- I like it. It was memorable.
- Promise?

00:37:26.856 --> 00:37:30.484
It's just not that soundproof.

00:37:30.860 --> 00:37:33.320
But it was okay, not bad.

00:37:34.321 --> 00:37:36.282
Are you really okay?
You really look flushed.

00:37:36.282 --> 00:37:40.327
Me? No, I'm fine.

00:37:40.578 --> 00:37:43.414
The design is beautiful.
You did this?

00:37:43.414 --> 00:37:44.415
Yes, I did it.

00:37:44.415 --> 00:37:46.041
All right, let's eat.

00:37:46.041 --> 00:37:47.543
Come on. Let's eat.

00:37:48.092 --> 00:37:49.719
The food looks good.

00:37:51.547 --> 00:37:52.298
Delicious.

00:37:52.298 --> 00:37:54.633
- Maybe Architect Diaz is already hungry.
- Braised pork.

00:37:58.629 --> 00:38:00.364
The adobo really looks good, Dan.

00:38:00.389 --> 00:38:01.891
Thanks for the recommendation.

00:38:02.600 --> 00:38:04.101
You're welcome, Clea.

00:38:04.226 --> 00:38:06.145
You know, I actually know
a lot more good places to eat.

00:38:06.145 --> 00:38:07.566
I can recommend more next time.

00:38:07.938 --> 00:38:09.398
I'll take note of that.

00:38:11.901 --> 00:38:13.360
Do you like it, Via?

00:38:14.653 --> 00:38:15.534
Huh?

00:38:16.447 --> 00:38:18.866
That's so inappropriate.

00:38:18.866 --> 00:38:19.948
Huh?

00:38:20.727 --> 00:38:22.312
I was talking about the food.

00:38:24.128 --> 00:38:25.880
Is it good?

00:38:26.165 --> 00:38:28.667
Does it taste good to you?

00:38:30.169 --> 00:38:32.505
Yes. It's delicious.

00:38:32.922 --> 00:38:34.632
I like the food.

00:38:34.632 --> 00:38:36.008
You like it?

00:38:37.885 --> 00:38:39.804
You were right, though.

00:38:39.804 --> 00:38:41.305
Not that.

00:38:41.305 --> 00:38:43.933
I'm talking about the sex.

00:38:46.727 --> 00:38:49.230
Ouch!

00:38:50.147 --> 00:38:50.856
Hey!

00:38:50.856 --> 00:38:52.107
Are you okay?

00:38:53.901 --> 00:38:56.403
There are so
many big ants here.

00:38:57.321 --> 00:38:58.072
It's so itchy.

00:39:00.366 --> 00:39:01.200
Ouch.

00:39:07.122 --> 00:39:08.265
Adi?

00:39:10.125 --> 00:39:11.502
Hi, love!

00:39:11.502 --> 00:39:13.570
- Hi, love.
- I missed you.

00:39:13.651 --> 00:39:14.709
Hi.

00:39:16.674 --> 00:39:18.258
He is Clea's boyfriend?

00:39:19.343 --> 00:39:20.719
Yeah. It's been a while.

00:39:20.886 --> 00:39:22.513
No way. Seriously?

00:39:22.778 --> 00:39:24.363
Then how did they
manage to hide it?

00:39:24.557 --> 00:39:29.186
Well, they just know
what needs to be protected.

00:39:38.377 --> 00:39:40.588
I just don't wanna
be in your spotlight,

00:39:41.448 --> 00:39:43.284
so just leave me alone.

00:40:02.219 --> 00:40:06.348
Arkin, is it true that you and
Clea are building a house together?

00:40:07.641 --> 00:40:08.934
A house?

00:40:09.727 --> 00:40:10.936
That's not true.

00:40:11.103 --> 00:40:12.104
I'm single.

00:40:12.521 --> 00:40:14.189
And I'm not dating Clea.

00:40:14.899 --> 00:40:17.484
I don't know where that news came from,

00:40:17.484 --> 00:40:21.780
but as far as I know, Clea is really
building a new house right now.

00:40:21.780 --> 00:40:24.783
So I'm really proud of her
because she worked hard for that.

00:40:24.808 --> 00:40:27.811
But I have nothing to
do with it. That's all her.

00:40:28.842 --> 00:40:32.637
At least he doesn't have
to lie about it anymore.

00:40:38.543 --> 00:40:42.259
How do they even do that?
Keeping everything hidden?

00:40:50.100 --> 00:40:54.980
Via, can we meet? I want to
discuss the furnishing and other details.

00:40:57.733 --> 00:41:00.361
Sure. Just tell me when and where.

00:41:05.728 --> 00:41:08.773
Sorry, Architect, I had
to bring Adi with me today.

00:41:08.945 --> 00:41:10.529
My car's getting fixed.

00:41:10.704 --> 00:41:13.165
No, it's fine. No worries.

00:41:14.166 --> 00:41:15.793
Excuse me, I'll just
use the restroom, okay?

00:41:15.793 --> 00:41:17.336
- Yeah.
- Wait a sec.

00:41:25.135 --> 00:41:27.429
Architect, how are you?

00:41:27.972 --> 00:41:30.265
Aren't you Larkin's girlfriend?

00:41:34.019 --> 00:41:37.189
I'm doing fine.

00:41:39.692 --> 00:41:41.527
Good thing the media
hasn't spotted you.

00:41:41.986 --> 00:41:44.071
It's fine. We don't really care.

00:41:50.035 --> 00:41:54.456
Can I ask you something about you and Clea?

00:41:55.290 --> 00:41:56.291
Sure.

00:41:59.128 --> 00:42:01.797
Are you okay with Clea being
in a love team with Arkin?

00:42:02.464 --> 00:42:03.524
I mean,

00:42:03.549 --> 00:42:04.967
don't you ever get jealous?

00:42:05.926 --> 00:42:07.004
Because...

00:42:07.601 --> 00:42:10.563
it's okay for people to
see them together in public,

00:42:11.265 --> 00:42:14.685
but you two have
to keep things low-key.

00:42:16.895 --> 00:42:20.149
You know, Clea's actually
the jealous one.

00:42:21.608 --> 00:42:23.027
We're not hiding.

00:42:23.777 --> 00:42:25.320
It's fine if people see us.

00:42:26.321 --> 00:42:29.116
Clea having a boyfriend
who isn't Arkin

00:42:29.742 --> 00:42:31.994
doesn't really affect
her career much now.

00:42:33.662 --> 00:42:36.707
It's not in their contract
anymore to be a love team,

00:42:36.707 --> 00:42:40.377
so they don't have
to pretend they're together.

00:42:41.920 --> 00:42:44.465
Clea and I just
decided to keep it low-key

00:42:44.965 --> 00:42:46.592
because they have
a movie right now.

00:42:49.968 --> 00:42:51.059
So...

00:42:52.222 --> 00:42:57.352
you're really okay seeing
them together in public?

00:43:01.523 --> 00:43:03.942
Before, I would've said no.

00:43:06.779 --> 00:43:07.946
But now,

00:43:10.240 --> 00:43:11.742
I guess I'm okay with it.

00:43:12.117 --> 00:43:16.580
I've learned to accept that
it comes with being with Clea.

00:43:19.792 --> 00:43:23.504
And if she's happy
under the spotlight,

00:43:24.379 --> 00:43:26.882
then I'll gladly
stand there with her.

00:43:29.176 --> 00:43:30.097
You know,

00:43:31.929 --> 00:43:33.514
I really admire her.

00:43:37.893 --> 00:43:43.690
There's a lot of unfair treatment
toward women in this industry.

00:43:48.445 --> 00:43:49.613
But that's just me.

00:43:50.489 --> 00:43:52.366
You have a different journey, Via.

00:43:53.158 --> 00:43:58.038
Especially if you're not fully ready
to be under the spotlight.

00:44:03.001 --> 00:44:04.503
Maybe that's true.

00:44:07.047 --> 00:44:10.217
Maybe I just can't...

00:44:12.553 --> 00:44:14.680
completely absorb all of it yet.

00:44:16.765 --> 00:44:18.183
I understand you.

00:44:19.893 --> 00:44:22.396
I know what happened
was very traumatizing.

00:44:23.488 --> 00:44:29.661
But you don't have to feel bad
or guilty if you're not okay yet.

00:44:29.945 --> 00:44:30.904
Take your time.

00:44:32.865 --> 00:44:35.367
I can see how much Arkin loves you.

00:44:35.576 --> 00:44:37.035
And I'm sure

00:44:37.661 --> 00:44:40.247
he'll wait until you're all okay.

00:44:47.004 --> 00:44:48.422
Thank you, Adi.

00:44:52.342 --> 00:44:53.177
Do you want some?

00:44:53.177 --> 00:44:54.136
I'm good.

00:44:54.136 --> 00:44:55.092
Sure?

00:44:55.637 --> 00:44:56.553
Coffee?

00:44:59.641 --> 00:45:01.059
Hey, I'm back.

00:45:01.935 --> 00:45:03.020
How are you?

00:45:03.187 --> 00:45:04.217
Okay?

00:45:06.023 --> 00:45:06.982
Okay, let's start.

00:45:07.441 --> 00:45:08.327
Yeah.

00:45:08.358 --> 00:45:10.068
So, I just wanna update you-

00:45:10.068 --> 00:45:10.874
Okay.

00:45:11.153 --> 00:45:13.739
with the progress
of our construction.

00:45:26.752 --> 00:45:31.089
So in the next few weeks,
let's start looking for furniture.

00:45:31.089 --> 00:45:34.384
That way, when the house
is ready and finished,

00:45:34.384 --> 00:45:36.803
we'll just wait for the delivery
and then have everything installed.

00:45:36.803 --> 00:45:38.096
Okay. Perfect.

00:45:42.017 --> 00:45:44.728
By the way, when do you
plan on directing a film?

00:45:46.605 --> 00:45:48.315
Maybe after I graduate.

00:45:48.960 --> 00:45:52.236
I've already made some
short films for school projects.

00:45:52.819 --> 00:45:55.822
One of them even won at a film festival.

00:45:57.991 --> 00:45:59.785
That's really impressive.

00:46:00.661 --> 00:46:05.707
At least you're still doing something
you love aside from music.

00:46:08.669 --> 00:46:09.836
What about you?

00:46:10.526 --> 00:46:13.445
When are you going to
resign and start writing songs?

00:46:17.302 --> 00:46:18.512
I can't.

00:46:19.137 --> 00:46:20.514
It's not practical.

00:46:21.098 --> 00:46:25.602
You know I'm putting my siblings
through school and helping Papa.

00:46:26.895 --> 00:46:28.814
And if I do this,

00:46:29.523 --> 00:46:31.275
I'd be starting from scratch.

00:46:31.858 --> 00:46:33.360
No connections.

00:46:34.486 --> 00:46:36.321
I'm not even that good yet.

00:46:36.738 --> 00:46:38.156
Who would even
take a chance on me?

00:46:41.243 --> 00:46:42.274
I would.

00:46:44.175 --> 00:46:45.509
Write music with me.

00:46:45.973 --> 00:46:47.474
I will pay you more than enough.

00:46:47.499 --> 00:46:48.797
Just what you deserve.

00:46:49.584 --> 00:46:50.703
Kino.

00:46:51.003 --> 00:46:53.422
Yeah, I'm serious. Do you
want us to start now?

00:46:53.422 --> 00:46:54.881
I'm writing a song.

00:46:57.009 --> 00:46:58.218
About what?

00:47:00.095 --> 00:47:01.388
Well...

00:47:02.973 --> 00:47:04.141
About us.

00:47:05.058 --> 00:47:09.146
I want to tell our story, how we
started and how we ended.

00:47:10.647 --> 00:47:15.402
That's why I was hoping you'd
be with me while I write it.

00:47:16.903 --> 00:47:18.322
Via, can we?

00:47:20.741 --> 00:47:21.783
Okay.

00:47:22.701 --> 00:47:23.827
Let's try.

00:47:24.119 --> 00:47:25.329
All right.

00:47:25.787 --> 00:47:28.540
Wait, my notebook's at my condo.

00:47:28.540 --> 00:47:29.666
Let's grab it first.

00:47:29.916 --> 00:47:31.335
- Let's go?
- Let's go.

00:47:31.335 --> 00:47:32.282
Okay.

00:47:34.929 --> 00:47:35.930
Okay, let's go.

00:47:37.299 --> 00:47:38.314
Let's go.

00:47:54.316 --> 00:47:56.193
Surprise!

00:47:56.193 --> 00:47:58.904
Congratulations, Larkin!

00:47:59.654 --> 00:48:01.073
Who's that?

00:48:02.772 --> 00:48:04.649
Larkin, who's that with you?

00:48:06.223 --> 00:48:07.224
Larkin!

00:48:07.662 --> 00:48:09.873
Oh my gosh.
Isn't she the side chick?

00:48:09.873 --> 00:48:11.166
What is she doing here?

00:48:12.466 --> 00:48:13.676
Is that her?

00:48:13.978 --> 00:48:15.897
Larkin, who's that with you?

00:48:15.922 --> 00:48:17.090
Larkin, Larkin!

00:48:17.935 --> 00:48:19.103
Larkin, who is she?

00:48:21.301 --> 00:48:23.804
Isn't that the girl who-

00:48:23.804 --> 00:48:26.264
The one who stole him from Clea?

00:48:26.306 --> 00:48:28.225
Isn't she the girl from before?

00:48:28.266 --> 00:48:29.184
Hey! It really is Larkin!

00:48:29.184 --> 00:48:30.435
Come on!

00:48:30.435 --> 00:48:31.895
- Is it really him?
- Larkin!

00:48:31.895 --> 00:48:33.146
Larkin! Take a photo with us!

00:48:33.628 --> 00:48:34.958
You're just a side chick!

00:48:37.038 --> 00:48:40.124
- Larkin!
- Larkin!

00:48:51.665 --> 00:48:52.692
Via?

00:48:55.074 --> 00:48:58.668
Tell your sister, she has
no right to ruin ArClea!

00:48:58.693 --> 00:49:00.028
What did you just say?

00:49:00.053 --> 00:49:01.137
Mira?

00:49:01.162 --> 00:49:03.665
- Hey, what are you doing-
- Mira!

00:49:09.260 --> 00:49:11.762
Didn't I tell you not to
bother me when I'm writing?

00:49:11.974 --> 00:49:12.934
I'll deal with that later.

00:49:14.929 --> 00:49:15.638
Via?

00:49:15.663 --> 00:49:17.790
I called security. They won't be
able to follow us anymore.

00:49:17.815 --> 00:49:19.316
Via? Via.

00:49:20.527 --> 00:49:22.279
Via, calm down, okay?

00:49:22.304 --> 00:49:24.556
I'm sorry, I didn't know
that was gonna happen.

00:49:26.099 --> 00:49:30.537
I promise I won't let anything
bad happen to you, okay?

00:49:30.829 --> 00:49:32.289
Please listen to me.

00:49:42.757 --> 00:49:45.010
You're really so far away now, Arkin.

00:49:48.847 --> 00:49:50.557
Via, just listen to me.

00:49:50.822 --> 00:49:54.409
I love you. I'll protect you
no matter what happens.

00:49:54.936 --> 00:49:56.396
It's different now.

00:49:57.898 --> 00:50:00.400
Please trust me. Stay with me.

00:50:01.359 --> 00:50:02.569
Via, please.

00:50:06.531 --> 00:50:10.076
Kino, when will my
love ever be enough?

00:50:14.418 --> 00:50:16.586
Please trust me on this, okay? I'm sorry.

00:51:23.567 --> 00:51:25.318
Is she the one you were telling me about?

00:51:25.460 --> 00:51:26.545
Yeah, that's her.

00:51:26.570 --> 00:51:28.655
Why is she trending?
Because she's a slut?

00:51:28.655 --> 00:51:29.364
You said it.

00:51:29.364 --> 00:51:30.073
Definitely.

00:51:30.115 --> 00:51:34.661
Videos and photos of you with a woman
at your condo are spreading online.

00:51:34.744 --> 00:51:36.371
The girl who supposedly seduced me,

00:51:37.372 --> 00:51:40.208
the girl who tried to fight Clea,
and all the other stories out there-

00:51:40.208 --> 00:51:44.379
I want that when
people hear the song I wrote,

00:51:44.379 --> 00:51:48.967
they'll feel how light my heart
was while I was writing it.

00:51:49.776 --> 00:51:54.531
You don't really say anything
when you're not okay.

00:51:59.953 --> 00:52:02.038
I'm flying back
to Spain next week.

00:52:02.063 --> 00:52:03.690
Are you coming back?

00:52:19.080 --> 00:52:20.332
Arkin?

00:52:20.332 --> 00:52:21.363
Via.